<!-- ===================== FAQ ===================== -->
<section class="section-pad surface-cream2" style="padding-top:0" data-screen-label="FAQ">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="faq__head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow center" style="justify-content:center">Questions, answered</p>
      <h2>The owner FAQ.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq__list" data-faq>
      <div class="faq__item is-open" data-faq-item><button class="faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="true"><span>What does Cardo charge?</span><span class="faq__plus">+</span></button><div class="faq__panel"><p class="muted faq__a">A straight 20% of booking revenue — no setup fees, no monthly minimums, and no charge until your home is earning. Other full-service managers run 18–35%. Your exact scope is confirmed in your free property analysis.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq__item" data-faq-item><button class="faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>How fast can my home go live?</span><span class="faq__plus">+</span></button><div class="faq__panel"><p class="muted faq__a">Most homes launch within a few weeks: onboarding and permitting, in-house design and photography, listing build-out, and pricing setup before your first guest.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq__item" data-faq-item><button class="faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>Will I still control my calendar?</span><span class="faq__plus">+</span></button><div class="faq__panel"><p class="muted faq__a">Always. Block owner stays anytime from your dashboard. It's your home — we keep it performing when you're not using it.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq__item" data-faq-item><button class="faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>Do you handle San Diego STR permits and TOT?</span><span class="faq__plus">+</span></button><div class="faq__panel"><p class="muted faq__a">Yes — STRO licensing, compliance reporting, and transient occupancy tax filings so your home stays fully compliant.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq__item" data-faq-item><button class="faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>How do I see my numbers?</span><span class="faq__plus">+</span></button><div class="faq__panel"><p class="muted faq__a">A real-time owner dashboard plus itemized monthly statements. Every booking, payout, and expense, whenever you want it.</p></div></div>
    </div>
